description: Space Skellies are a group of intergalactic adventurers who explore the depths of the galaxy in search of new and exciting discoveries. On one of their adventures, they discover a mysterious artifact called ordinals, which is powered by bitcoin. This artifact holds a powerful secret that could revolutionize the way we view the universe. With the help of their trusty ship, the Space Skellies venture further into the unknown, uncovering clues and unlocking the secrets of the ordinals. Along the way, they also learn about the power of bitcoin and its potential for unlocking the mysteries of the universe.
name: Space Skelly Ordinals
